<Policy>
  <h1>Collection Development Policy</h1>
  <p>Waypoint Digital Library curates texts with significant scholarly value, emphasizing the humanities and the long nineteenth century. Selection prioritizes rights-clear works that can be improved with new editorial attention.</p>
  <h2>Selection Criteria</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Rights status permits open access distribution.</li>
    <li>Textual quality allows for an A-grade edition.</li>
    <li>Relevance to curricula and research priorities.</li>
  </ul>
</Policy>
